The '''Das'skar Hunting Mask''' was a type of mask that was created by the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]] for their [[Nikto/Legends|Nikto]] minions. Utilized especially by [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]], the masks improved the [[Sensor/Legends|sensory]] capabilities of the wearers, assisting them in tracking down their quarry.

